	  Size                Normal
	  Shape               Italic
	EndFont
End

# Acknowledgements style definition
Style Acknowledgements
	Margin                Dynamic
	LatexType             Command
	InTitle               0
	LatexName             acknowledgements
	TopSep                1.2     
	ParSkip               0.4
	BottomSep             0.8
